  "body": "Bump `transformers` and `sentence-transformers` lower bounds in `langchain-huggingface` to resolve a dependency conflict with `huggingface-hub` 1.x. The existing constraints allowed `huggingface-hub>=0.33.4,<2.0.0` (so hub 1.x is valid), but `transformers` 4.x requires `huggingface-hub<1.0` \u2014 causing the pre-release CI job to fail when `uv pip install --force-reinstall` resolved hub to 1.5.0 while leaving `transformers` at 4.56.2.\r\n\r\nBreaking change for users on transformers 4.x or sentence-transformers<5.2.0 who install langchain-huggingface[full].",
